---
---
<section class="relative min-h-[130vh] pt-[64px] pb-48 flex items-center overflow-hidden" style="background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #6A0DAD 0%, #0A0A0F 70%);">
<!-- Logo as full-section background -->
<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
<img alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover mix-blend-lighten opacity-25" src="/images/logo.jpg"/>
</div>
<div class="absolute inset-0 scanline-overlay z-10 opacity-30"></div>
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-20 w-full">
<div class="max-w-xl space-y-8">
<h1 class="font-barlow font-black text-6xl md:text-8xl leading-none tracking-tight uppercase" style="color: #f9f5fd;">
                    JOUW RETRO <br/>
<span style="color: #9b5fe0;">GAMING PARADIJS</span>
</h1>
<p style="color: #acaab1;" class="text-lg max-w-lg font-body leading-relaxed">
                    Herbeleef de gouden jaren van gaming. Van zeldzame NES-cartridges tot legendarische PlayStation-klassiekers — exclusief tweedehands, uitvoerig getest.
                </p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-2">
<button class="font-orbitron font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-sm neon-glow transform hover:scale-105 transition-all uppercase tracking-widest text-sm" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #9b5fe0, #8b4fd0); color: #f9f5fd;">
                        Bekijk Aanbod
                    </button>
<button class="font-orbitron font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-sm hover:opacity-80 transition-all uppercase tracking-widest text-sm backdrop-blur-sm" style="border: 1px solid rgba(72,71,77,0.4); background: rgba(31,31,38,0.5); color: #f9f5fd;">
                        Inruilen
                    </button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Scrolling Ticker -->
<div class="absolute top-[64px] w-full backdrop-blur-sm py-3 overflow-hidden z-30" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.8); border-top: 1px solid rgba(155,95,224,0.2); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(155,95,224,0.2);">
<div class="ticker-scroll flex items-center gap-12 font-orbitron text-sm font-bold tracking-[0.3em]" style="color: #9b5fe0;">
<span>NES · SNES · N64 · PS1 · PS2 · XBOX · SEGA · GAMEBOY · ATARI · DREAMCAST · GAME CUBE · WII · NEO GEO · COMMODORE 64</span>
<span>NES · SNES · N64 · PS1 · PS2 · XBOX · SEGA · GAMEBOY · ATARI · DREAMCAST · GAME CUBE · WII · NEO GEO · COMMODORE 64</span>
</div>
</div>
</section>
